Klasse EmployeeGUI

java.lang.Object
com.wegapplikation.config.view.EmployeeGUI
public class EmployeeGUI extends Object
Represents the main graphical user interface (GUI) for the Employee/User level of the pathfinding application. This class sets up the main application frame, the map panel (RouteCal), and controls for pathfinding input, path calculation, and login access.
